item.description:
Website: www.eastwindsor-ct.gov

8:00 a.m. Packet pickup and late registration
9:30 a.m. Veterans Day memorial service
10:00 a.m. 5K start

$11 fee until 10/31, $15 afterwards.

Directions: I-91 to exit 45 to Rt 140 East toward Warehouse Point/Ellington. Follow 140 East for approximately 3.8 miles, then turn right at the light onto Rt 191/Main Street. Keep going straight (Main St becomes Rye St) for approximately 1 mile. Bear right at the fork in front of St. Catherine's Church. Town hall and parking will be on your left.

Please bring a non-perishable food item to the race.
item.how_to_find_us: We can meet in front of the Town Hall just before 9:30.
item.name: East Windsor Veterans Day 5K
